description:
Archaeology and Jesus Episode 2: The Sealed Locus
Master the techniques of archaeology by cracking open a sealed floor of an ancient city, while uncovering newly discovered evidence about life in the hometown of Jesus.

No place on earth has arrested the attention of adventurers and archaeologists like the Holy Land. But does what we dig up in Israel bear resemblance to the stories that we read about Jesus in the Gospels? To answer this question, Archaeology & Jesus follows two paths. Youll explore the process of archaeology with the top experts digging in Israel today. And along the way youll join New Testament scholar Dr. Craig Evans as he reveals groundbreaking finds that illuminate the life, death, and resurrection of Jesus.
